h2 Examples
p.-text
  | To render a search input, apply the class <code>chi-search__input</code> to an <code>input type="search"</code>.

h3 Base
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--3
    .chi-grid
      .chi-col.-w--12.-w-sm--8.-w-md--6.-w-lg--5
        .chi-form__item
          chi-label(for="example__base") Label
          chi-search-input(id="example__base")
          
  .example-tabs.-pl--2
    ul.chi-tabs#example-base
      li.-active
        a(href=`#webcomponent-base`) Web Component
      li
        a(href=`#html-base`) HTML Blueprint
  .chi-tabs-panel.-active#webcomponent-base
    :code(lang="html")
      <div class="chi-form__item">
        <chi-label for="example__base">Label</chi-label>
        <chi-search-input id="example__base"></chi-search-input>
      </div>
  .chi-tabs-panel#html-base
    :code(lang="html")
      <div class="chi-form__item">
        <label class="chi-label" for="example__base">Label</label>
        <div class="chi-input__wrapper -icon--right">
          <input class="chi-input chi-search__input" id="example__base" type="search" />
          <button class="chi-button -icon -flat -bg--none">
            <div class="chi-button__content">
              <i class="chi-icon icon-search"></i>
            </div>
          </button>
          <button class="chi-button -icon -close" aria-label="Close">
            <div class="chi-button__content">
              <i class="chi-icon icon-x"></i>
            </div>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      
h3 Disabled
p.-text
  | Use the <code>disabled</code> boolean attribute to prevent users from interacting with a search input.
  | Disabled inputs are not submitted with the form and can not receive any browsing events such as mouse clicks or focus.
  | <strong>Note:</strong> The required attribute can not be used on inputs with a disabled attribute specified.
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--3
    .chi-grid
      .chi-col.-w--12.-w-sm--8.-w-md--6.-w-lg--5
        .chi-form__item
          chi-label(for="example__disabled") Label
          chi-search-input(id="example__disabled" value="Sample text" disabled)

  .example-tabs.-pl--2
    ul.chi-tabs#example-disabled
      li.-active
        a(href=`#webcomponent-disabled`) Web Component
      li
        a(href=`#html-disabled`) HTML Blueprint
  .chi-tabs-panel.-active#webcomponent-disabled
    :code(lang="html")
